HEADWORD: Roe
<hw>Roe</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>ro</ets>, AS.
<ets>r⟦amac⟧h</ets>; akin to D. <ets>ree</ets>, G. <ets>reh</ets>, Icel.
